com.stormpath.sdk.servlet.event

Class RequestEventListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stormpath.sdk.servlet.event.RequestEventListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RequestEventListener

    public class RequestEventListenerAdapter
extends Object
implements RequestEventListener
    Default adapter implementation of the RequestEventListener interface, to be used to subclass and override only the methods necessary.

    All method implementations simply log to DEBUG.

    Since:
    1.0.RC3
